- Y' ≡ Y·Z (mod p)
- Z' ≡ Z² (mod p)
- T' ≡ X·Y (mod p)
where p = 2^255 - 19
These formulas implement the (division-free) conversion from projective ℙ² coordinates to extended
twisted Edwards ℙ³ coordinates.
-/
