- X' ≡ X·Z (mod p)
- Y' ≡ Y·Z (mod p)
- Z' ≡ Z² (mod p)
- T' ≡ X·Y (mod p)

Note: We compute the output representation (XZ, YZ, Z², XY) instead of the equivalent
